And for the other poster, I use 61 air almost exclusively. It might have stunned one and I got lucky with the combat round of the other, but the no delay between the 2 commands gets the pet at least 1 attack, taunt or cast on the add normally. Hitting twice is practically guaranteed to get an add on the pet.<br>
