<br>
Caveats: Firebolt of Tallon only unless it's a pretty weak mob heh.  You want it dead asap.  You MUST have a corner or other area to back into so you don't move back when hit.  Don't try it unless you can't perform the pet techniques, or move anywhere, such as when that will just buy you more aggro.  But it can be done if you have to do it.<br>
