<br>
Occasionally I've had to chain pets on 3 mobs.  It's extremely inefficient mana-wise, but as long as you aren't doing any nuking (aside from a kill shot, perhaps) it isn't THAT hard to keep the beasties on the pet.  Sometimes you're better off just gating.  It depends on how much of a pain it will be to get back to your camp and how calm you can remain while being pounded on. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
